Description: Aptura Plasma desktop integration
 Installs Aptura's KDE Plasma integration, desktop launchers, and utility hooks.
 The default desktop uses KDE Plasma with Aptura contextual branding,
 practical workstation tools, firmware visibility, power controls,
 local journey/context tooling, and a local system health check.
